{"tid":1224842,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"陶傑： 一句「暫緩」就了結？","createTime":"2019-06-15T05:12:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-15T09:13:53.000Z","uid":70115,"like":2107,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":127,"replies":[{"pid":"c4d6d210d4334d1ce4404110c3627453ba7b8f2a","tid":1224842,"uid":70115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T05:12:21.000Z","msg":"一句「暫緩」就了結？<br />\n<br />\n一個劫匪，持刀闖進一戶家庭，企圖搶劫，被全家人奮起抗擊，衝突其間，乒乒乓乓的打爛了許多傢俬和瓷器，打傷了幾個孩子。<br />\n<br />\n幸因家庭兄弟姐妹人丁眾多，團結抵抗，劫匪不得逞，疲累不堪，忽停下來，說：「我暫緩」，叫你開門放他（她）出去休息。<br />\n<br />\n中港和世界各國的法制，會不會讓該人抽身離場而不加引渡的道理？<br />\n<br />\n那麼香港蟻民還該下跪感謝該狼外婆暫停暴力搶掠、高抬貴手之恩，並為嚴重冒犯了一個慈母及其打手而向她（牠）道歉賠償精神損失呢？"},{"pid":"efa3a4b9072cedd88a98ea4549ef1c019d9eb2c3","tid":1224842,"uid":60924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T05:13:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d68d68060fd2af2905fd9cf8a286515ff76d061d","tid":1224842,"uid":54303,"like":115,"dislike":0,"score":115,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T05:13:38.000Z","msg":"不撤不散<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fcdb5a221b8762b7e9fde0e01e494388c6b96537","tid":1224842,"uid":51701,"like":45,"dislike":1,"score":44,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T05:13:59.000Z","msg":"直線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14a88b304cdbd9e6d6114781e7a820a77d167245","tid":1224842,"uid":105693,"like":168,"dislike":0,"score":168,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T05:15:20.000Z","msg":"一定要撤控所有無理被捕既示威人士<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b604e9745213088e0e5ec5fac905ed651181dc2e","tid":1224842,"uid":90601,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T05:21:16.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.co