 violet;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">香港最需要班KOL既時候，佢地就唔出黎。淨係放下story講支持就攞光環!<br />\n對唔對住612班義示!!!  食胡椒噴霧、食催淚彈、什至係食子彈呀！！！！ <br />\n自己係冷氣房share下，就話自己係支持香港，你哋班垃圾收唔收恥呀？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">一齊呼籲香港KOL清晰表明立場去發聲！</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">急！！需要大家幫手！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1219585\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1219585</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n你好，<br />\n作為香港既KOL, 係應該做Key Opinion Leader應該做既事！<br />\n如果你是支持這次香港的抗爭運動，希望你能夠發揮不同角色的作用，係你既網絡平台上發聲！<br />\n<br />\n作歌既可以作歌，拍片既可以拍片，寫文既可以寫文。<br />\n但絕對唔係求其出個story, 影下地下，影下天空，就話自己緊張香港。<br />\n<br />\n亦希望你清楚表明自己的立場，不是食大茶飯講d唔講d, 而係真真正正講出你對引渡法既睇法！<br />\n<br />\n當你口說支持，但又沒有就著KOL的角色，在網絡平台沒有就香港的抗爭作出清晰的回應和表明立場，身為Key Opinion Leader, 你慚愧嗎？"},{"pid":"78958f53d9acfc87c0befd85a28af7fd0c947051","tid":1224842,"uid":109646,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T05:46:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XVJ2Mp5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXVJ2Mp5.png&h=69863e51&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9f017c894e347b69ddbffbf5742961ec7fffa2ac","tid":1224842,"uid":26333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T05:47:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />19"},{"pid":"ad3ae94a1cfb795cbee2875801fc1865f8dc48fe","tid":1224842,"uid":156509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T05:47:41.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" clas